		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Predictive dialer</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>A <b>predictive dialer</b> is a computerized system that automatically dials batches of <a href="/wiki/Telephone_number" title="Telephone number">telephone numbers</a> for connection to agents assigned to sales or other campaigns. Predictive dialers are widely used in <a href="/wiki/Call_center" title="Call center" class="mw-redirect">call centers</a>.</p>
